---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Legal Notice" description="Legal Notice of SAS AVIACO FRANCE">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative text-white py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
      <img 
        src="/copter/3.jpg" 
        alt="Helicopter" 
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/60 via-black/50 to-black/60"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="font-outfit font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl mb-4">
          Legal Notice
        </h1>
        <p class="font-outfit text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-100">
          Legal Information
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              1. Website Publisher
            </h2>
            <div class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed space-y-2">
              <p><strong>Company Name :</strong> SAS AVIACO FRANCE</p>
              <p><strong>Legal Form :</strong> Simplified Joint Stock Company</p>
              <p><strong>Registered Office :</strong> Marignane, France</p>
              <p><strong>Email :</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@aviaco.fr" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@aviaco.fr</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              2. Publication Director
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              The publication director is the legal representative of SAS AVIACO FRANCE.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              3. Hosting
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              The website is hosted by a technical service provider. For any information regarding hosting, please contact us at the email address indicated above.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              4. Intellectual Property
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              This entire website is subject to French and international legislation on copyright and intellectual property. All reproduction rights are reserved, including for downloadable documents and iconographic and photographic representations.
            </p>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              The reproduction of all or part of this website on an electronic or other medium is strictly prohibited except with express authorization from the publication director.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              5. Personal Data Protection
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              In accordance with the French Data Protection Act of January 6, 1978, as amended, and the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), you have the right to access, rectify, delete, and object to personal data concerning you.
            </p>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              To exercise this right, you can contact us at the email address : <a href="mailto:contact@aviaco.fr" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@aviaco.fr</a>
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              6. Cookies
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              This website uses cookies to improve user experience and analyze traffic. By continuing to browse this website, you accept the use of cookies in accordance with our privacy policy.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              7. Limitation of Liability
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              The information contained on this website is as accurate as possible and the website is periodically updated, but may nevertheless contain inaccuracies, omissions, or gaps. If you notice a gap, error, or what appears to be a malfunction, please report it by email to <a href="mailto:contact@aviaco.fr" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@aviaco.fr</a>.
            </p>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              SAS AVIACO FRANCE cannot be held responsible for direct and indirect damage caused to the user's equipment when accessing the website, resulting either from the use of equipment that does not meet specifications, or from the appearance of a bug or incompatibility.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              8. Hyperlinks
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              The website may contain hyperlinks to other sites on the Internet. Links to these other resources take you away from the website. It is possible to create a link to the presentation page of this website without express authorization from the publisher. No authorization or prior information request may be required by the publisher from a website that wishes to establish a link to the publisher's website.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              9. Applicable Law
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              This legal notice is governed by French law. In case of dispute and in the absence of an amicable agreement, the dispute will be brought before the French courts in accordance with the rules of jurisdiction in force.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              10. Contact
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              For any questions regarding this legal notice, you can contact us at the following address : <a href="mailto:contact@aviaco.fr" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@aviaco.fr</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

